--------------------------------------------------
- README
--------------------------------------------------

Multiplayer pong!

We assume that users will not cheat

Frontend
--------------------------------------------------

JSON messages:

all don't strictly need the player field, can infer from server side

Leaves a screen
{type:"screen", player:#id, direction:"left" or "right"}
Bounces
{type:"bounce", player:#id, velocity:{x:#,y:#}, screen:{w:#,h:#}}
End Game
{type:"drop", player:#id}
Score change
{type:"score", player:#id, score:#}
